          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-03-08 21:37:14" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to become both dark and gloomy, with the implication of threatening</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to become dark and gloomy</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In order to combine the components of στυγνάζω, which involve not only darkness but also gloom and threatening, it may be possible to translate as ‘dark and threatening’ or ‘so dark as to cause one to be afraid.’</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
