          </LEXSubDomains>
          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-03-08 21:37:14" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to experience an emotional state of both grief and discouragement, as evidenced in the appearance of one’s face</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to be downcast</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to look gloomy</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to understand στυγνάζω in {S:04101002200006} as meaning ‘to be shocked, to be appalled’ (see {D:25.222}).</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
